CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 1, 1956, pg. A11 reads: "Wins Wardrobe - "Ed" Alexander of Alexander's, 6121 Penn Ave., presents a certificate for a complete wardrobe to Mildred Ann Briscoe, winner of the "Miss WILY" contest. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "Ed" Alexander presenting wardrobe certificate to "Miss WILY" Mildred Ann Briscoe, posed in Warner's Cinerama Theatre
